    <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
      <h2> SPDXLicense</h2> 
      <div> 
        <p> The license that applies to an Implementation Guide (using an SPDX license Identifiers,
           or 'not-open-source'). The binding is required but new SPDX license Identifiers are allowed
           to be used (https://spdx.org/licenses/).</p> 

      </div> 
      <p> This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/spdx-license defines the following codes:</p>
